episodes.title: Francesca Fiorentini Takes Down MAGA Cultist Tulsi Gabbard!
episodes.description:
In this enthralling video, Francesca Fiorentini and a guest discussed the possibility that Tulsi Gabbard may be in a cult. Francesca's guest - a journalist who covers cults - explained that Tulsi Gabbard's parents were in a cult which Tulsi never left.

On Francesca Fiorentini's show, The Bitchuation Room, they broke down how this may affect Tulsi's involvement with Donald Trump's cabinet. Could there be a tug of war behind the cult leader that Tulsi Gabbard grew up with and the biggest cult leader in the world - the head of the cult of MAGA?

This is a must-see video to see this case made. Francesca Fiorentini is sure to continue to cover the wackiness of figures like Tulsi Gabbard and all the other kooks involved with MAGA.
